<L>Shall ch<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">at them of their natural joys,</L>
<L>Nor &s;hall they more, by artifice &s;ubdued,</L>
<L>Ki&s;s the oppre&s;&s;or's rod, "A SWINISH MULTITUDE."</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Have not the titled &s;ons of earth,</L>
<L>U&s;urp<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d prerogative of birth;</L>
