</LG>
<LG>
<L>Far other &s;hone fair Freedom's band,</L>
<L>Far other was the immortal &s;tand,</L>
<L>When Hamp<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">en fought for thee:</L>
<L>They &s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">te<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">'d from rapine's grief thy &s;poils,</L>
