<PB N="239" REF="240">Borromu.</HI> 2. BLESSED STUFFS! found in the Shrine of <HI>St. Dennis.</HI> 3. Papers to PROVE that the RELICS of <HI>St. Vincent</HI> are GENUINE. 4. A TOOTH of the LOWER <HI>Jaw</HI> of St. Vincent. 5. A <HI>Bit</HI> of the HEAD and the <HI>Hair</HI> of <HI>St. Guignelot.</HI> 6. A PIECE of the ROBE of the HOLY <HI>Virgin.</HI> 7. A PIECE of the FROCK of the <HI>Infant Je&s;us.</HI> 8. The SKULL of <HI>St. Seba&s;tian.</HI> 9. The GRIDIRON of <HI>St. Laurence.</HI> 10. A <HI>Piece</HI> of the TRUE <HI>Cro&s;s.</HI> 11. <HI>Two</HI> Vials of the MILK of the MOST <HI>Holy</HI> Virgin."</P>
